# Cursor indexing configuration template
# This file uses negation patterns to INCLUDE files that are gitignored
# but should still be indexed by Cursor Agent
#
# Note: Cursor respects .gitignore by default. These negation patterns
# override .gitignore exclusions to include specific files for indexing.
#
# Copy this file to your project root as `.cursorignore` and customize as needed.

# Documentation directories that are gitignored but contain useful context
!docs/adr/0001.md
!docs/notes/
!docs/notes/**/*
!docs/entrypoints.md
!docs/plans/
!docs/plans/**/*
!docs/tech-debt.md
!docs/todo-list.md
!docs/context/
!docs/context/**/*
!docs:context/
!docs:context/**/*
!docs/examples/
!docs/examples/**/*
!docs/ontology_applications/
!docs/ontology_applications/**/*

# AGENTS.md (gitignored but contains workspace rules)
!AGENTS.md

!.cursorignore

# .cursor directory (for cursor-specific configs)
!.cursor/
!.cursor/**/*
